s/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"964eea9fdbf6b72b1b831fb55cabf0d21b88fcea","tid":1082562,"uid":22701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T05:52:17.000Z","msg":"自辯加無悔意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"032ae1449212fe562e8d5e82ab06279d16066470","tid":1082562,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T05:56:31.000Z","msg":"偷咁少唔會震怒啦 放心"},{"pid":"3ca75683bac5c5a92c2b4fce612a0bb4c8900eb5","tid":1082562,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T08:27:20.000Z","msg":"杯麵、豆漿、牙刷<br />\n<br />\n監獄入面有，免費，唔使偷。阿sir你可以放心喺入面享用，順便同獄友一齊踢波，鑽研腳法球技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4697b00dd0ef73f6fa759c815881a07afe58b03","tid":1082562,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:07:20.000Z","msg":"漸漸覺得啲警察好多都似魔警<br />\n有反社會傾向"},{"pid":"7f118e1b93c40bc00fd68b643ecf549ac18b9935","tid":1082562,"uid":126219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:27:30.000Z","msg":"班警狗真係有鋪犯法癮"},{"pid":"8674f72aba8817d7f98390e9d514676c9fb6f11c","tid":1082562,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:32:44.000Z","msg":"警察犯罪率<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}